I was a wee bit skeptical at first as it appeared a bit too sweet, but 1/2 way through the reduction process (I used home grown tomatoes; Hence it had more liquid)....but much to ,my family's and my elation, it was perfect for the 4th of July festivities. Even the non-ketchup eaters gobbled it down!